AUDIO VISUAL
COMMUNICATION CENTER
February 21, 1967
National Educational Radio
1346 Connecticut Avenoe, N. W.
Washington, D. C. 20036
Re: Docket No. 20554
Dear Sir:
Enclosed is a copy of our letter to the Federal Communications
Commission regarding Docket No. 20554.
I regret that this letter has been so late; but due to the
lack of time at the end of December, this letter never got written.
Your latest newsletter stated that these letters could still be
written due to postponement of deadline.
I hope this one letter will make some small impression
in the decision by the Federal Communications Commission.
Wendell H. Dodds
Manager, KUNR-FM
